                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14151778" author="yukim" created="Mon, 29 Sep 2014 15:14:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like sstableloader is over releasing reference when &apos;-cph&apos; &amp;gt; 1.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;StreamCoordinator#sliceSSTableDetails&lt;/tt&gt; needs to remove content from given SSTablesStreamingSection when splitting as in &lt;tt&gt;StreamSession#addTransferFile&lt;/tt&gt;, so that the same SSTable does not get over-released after adding to StreamPlan (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.1/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/io/sstable/SSTableLoader.java#L195&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.1/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/io/sstable/SSTableLoader.java#L195&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14151798" author="jmckenzie" created="Mon, 29 Sep 2014 15:31:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14153371" author="yukim" created="Tue, 30 Sep 2014 16:41:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
